textBeforeTable: 1958 Chevrolet Yeoman Production Numbers   The Yeoman was a Station Wagon produced by Chevrolet for only one model year.  Built to appeal to the outdoorsy crowd, the Yeoman featured vinyl upholstery, rubber floor mats, and a linoleum platform to make the interior a breeze to wash.  A Yeoman could be purchased as either a 2-door or 4-door with the capacity to fit 6 passengers.  1958 Chevrolet Yeoman document.write(''); if(typeof(tile) == "undefined"){var tile = 1} else {tile++} if(typeof(dcopt) == "undefined"){var dcopt = "dcopt=ist;"} else {var dcopt = ""} if(typeof(cachebuster) == "undefined"){var cachebuster = Math.floor(Math.random()*10000000000)}
